Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.03,0:17:31.68,CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁現在越過紅線吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.28,0:17:33.14,CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.43,0:17:46.60,CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結束了 祈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.47,0:17:50.46,CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.21,0:17:55.98,CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.54,0:18:02.84,CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是想幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.86,0:18:03.55,CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.53,0:18:06.92,CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祈 你別過去
